WEBVTT

00:02:57.080 --> 00:03:00.280
the judgement will be in your favor,"

00:03:01.480 --> 00:03:05.560
irrespective of the fact
that there was no evidence whatsoever

00:03:06.480 --> 00:03:08.696
that I had any wrongdoing

00:03:08.720 --> 00:03:11.000
on the charges that I was up against.

00:03:13.280 --> 00:03:15.736
I remember the events

00:03:15.760 --> 00:03:17.616
of my conviction

00:03:17.640 --> 00:03:20.216
six years ago

00:03:20.240 --> 00:03:21.920
as if it were yesterday.

00:03:23.320 --> 00:03:26.896
The cold, hard face of the judge

00:03:26.920 --> 00:03:29.696
as she pronounced my sentence

00:03:29.720 --> 00:03:31.880
on a cold Thursday morning